-- Erste Group forecasts 2014 loss of 1.4-1.6 bln eur
-- By Michael Shields
-- Thu Jul 03, 2014 12:24PM EDT
-- None



VIENNA, July 3 (Reuters) - Austria's Erste Group Bank <ERST.VI> expects to lose up to 1.6 billion euros ($2.2 billion) this year given the need to boost provisions in Hungary and Romania, it said on Thursday.

